<h1 id="supporter">Become a Supporter</h1>

<p class="main-paragraph">Thank you for interest in contributing to Penpot!</p>

<h2 id="supporter-howto">How to become a Penpot Supporter</h2>
<p>If you’d like to contribute to the growth and development of Penpot, you can become a supporter. Your contribution helps us continue improving the platform for everyone.</p>

<p>To become a supporter, simply follow the link below and adjust the contribution amount to whatever feels right for you.</p>

<p class="advice">
Please note, becoming a supporter doesn’t come with any special benefits — it's simply a way to help us grow. Your support means a lot to us!
<br><br>
</p>
